textBeforeTable: Nearby Services Hampton's free hot breakfast Onsite Services Entertainment & Attractions View Entertainment & Attractions While you're in Town Once you arrive at the Hampton Inn & Suites Sarasota/Lakewood Ranch, talk to any member of our friendly team about the best time to visit local restaurants to enjoy the absolute freshest catch of the day you'll ever experience. Believe it or not, there are people who visit Sarasota who go out of their way to avoid the sand and experience Sarasota FL attractions. Golfers! Pack your clubs and test your swing against the public links at Legacy Golf Club, just minutes from the Hampton Inn & Suites® Sarasota/Lakewood Ranch. Treat yourself to a drive along Gulf of Mexico Drive, a highway that links Sarasota Key islands together and offers motorists unparalleled views of both Sarasota Bay and the Gulf of Mexico.
